Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最最不明白的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出要求的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要啊 他上身都脱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 如果说还是不要吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会害羞 你转过身去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这种时候了 不能再扭扭捏捏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好...好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没脱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢脱掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是...你帮我脱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么帮我脱...我在说什么蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这个时候 怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把头抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:03:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可...可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该看哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就想象一下这里是海边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在沙滩上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿着泳裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小七也换比基尼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 笑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...海边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海边 海边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕的话 到此为止也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让你后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 我想做让两个人开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的 不只是身体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不希望有一点点勉强的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我变成矢野的所有物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我也开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此...男孩子也会紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你同意...我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 好奇怪的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛的话 请举右手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是牙医吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七美有了可以奉献一切的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以奉献一切的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界任何东西都无法取代的重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他相遇一定是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不相信命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说...我在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇见了前所未有的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么美丽...耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像梦一样的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许 这只是现实一般的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 为什么穿着法披?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}法披=号衣 一种日本短式上衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是幸福的梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 穿法披的时候说的是别的话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是结婚仪式上新郎新娘的誓词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞礼物 给我一个承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是梦? 还是现实?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是现实 现实 现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...好痛 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手 右手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对不起高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想其他事情 分散下注意力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐的事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如...你正吃着最喜欢的肉包子 很幸福...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 快穿衣服 衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是书都在楼下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会拿给你 你先偷偷出去再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 她一定看到我鞋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没脸见你妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如在意下别的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是蠢到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 很好笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得好笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有我们的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 伤你自尊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我可是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你穿的真少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要失望啦 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想装酷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却逊成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得我们好像演戏一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是舞台 我们是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我变成矢野的所有物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才感到害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴 我喜欢的人是矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天一样算是我们的纪念日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初体验之日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊 我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么体验了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈那边没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可恶 老妈为什么这时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家绝对不可以再做这种事了 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前觉得 SEX只是种运动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它应该是件神圣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天来我家很认真地对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他哪根筋不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么爱现在的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和高桥做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥是他女朋友吗 我都没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是见过他牵着一个女生的手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:13:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆圆的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常普通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通到让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和奈奈的事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有点疗效吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在世界上的人 总要活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么活不活的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开心地过好今天就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要买特级酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 他以前和奈奈在一起时 也是少根筋的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千元整
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合算哦 不过只收现金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有漫天要价吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我花1万4千元买下的 几乎全新的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿过几次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两三次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脏兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用橡皮擦掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附送一顶帽子 外加某模型玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共一万元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还涨价呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野在卖东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 为什么 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只买鞋 3000元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7500元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3250元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6000元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3500元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再高不买了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3500休息费都不够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走投无路啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的one star我倒可以出八千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙平时都在看我的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑 那双不卖的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且八千也太便宜了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你拿到网上拍卖呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了 我需要现金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我买这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2000元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人心险恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看险恶的都是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才绑好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:15:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发 都乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球头绑成羊羹(日式糖果)状?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么球球羊羹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 最近有关于你的奇怪流言哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪流言?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你成了守财奴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了旅馆钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在家里还是危险了点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 也不知道父母什么时候出门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个...我想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己...不太喜欢情人旅馆之类的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七果然还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 上次太匆忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得第一次的感觉很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如干脆旅行去海边或泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能创造美好回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以创造回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆费 交通费
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是东京迪斯尼乐园就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一共多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加起来一共多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...我准备了这个 两人一起慢慢存钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过到时候享受的快乐也会加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个可以存到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了高桥的笑容 存钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要存上半年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业旅行之前应该能存到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我会想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 借我看 借我看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的幸福 也许曾经是属于别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存了多少钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,721元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天一起看焰火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一直是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庙会 雾之庆典 海边 全都要和矢野一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起创造很多很多回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢回忆这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的国语上过这样一课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的衣服是什么颜色的这一课
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A和B聊起以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后说起了挂在小学楼梯平台墙上的一幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幅画是一个女孩在夕阳下摘着花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A说 好怀念啊 是那幅黄衣服女孩的画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后B说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 那个女孩子穿的是被夕阳映红的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对是红的 不对不对 绝对是黄衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么我们去确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人来到了怀念的母校 心情激动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟女孩子穿的是什么颜色的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么颜色的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幅黑白画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴影浓重的人物上 只有用黑色涂满的衣服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而两人的记忆中衣服都是有色彩的 并且这样深信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 人类的记忆都是不牢靠的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有颜色 却涂上颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自点缀美化它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且赋予实际根本没有的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不相信所谓的美丽回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 绝对 小七
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我眼前的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 今天陪我逛街好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 都掉出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有这本书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本原来也读诗集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时见她只读些难懂的书
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会发现东西掉出来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办...不知不觉就拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点稚气 这是矢野 左边是竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这个人...大概就是奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么山本...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.19,0:25:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本没了照片 一定很着急
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.82,0:25:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...我的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.81,0:25:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷摸摸查别人的行为...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.23,0:25:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.18,0:25:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 为什么姐姐会在香川的车上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.02,0:25:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想知道吗

